{"title":"慕田峪长城","authors":["查干"],"dates":[{"year":1986,"month":9,"day":18}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"慕田峪长城"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"查干（蒙古族）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这一声战马悲壮的嘶鸣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"竟震落无数发光的星辰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"箭镞生锈　战神的梦也生锈"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无声倒在慕田峪的鸦翅下"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阔叶林一生代一生代的长着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抹不掉辽远迷离的狼烟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山峦起伏　心潮也起伏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山雨打在铃蓝花上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"燕山一片迷蒙"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我从八达岭一步迈到慕田峪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长城惊梦醒了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却不能圆它"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挽着妻子的手"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她不知为何而笑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说：垛口处生起的烟云"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是我为你在生炊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"劳驾，快脱下盔甲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拿起你的诗笔"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为和平祈祷新"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国的小学生"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一分钱一分钱的积攒着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也来修复这残缺的历史"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"面对慕田峪的明月"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们栽起现代人的骄傲和反思"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长天一碧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叶落无声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国，今夜你驻足何处？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在慕田峪的驿道上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我举一樽明月"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为你壮行"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}